==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gelatinate
<hw>Ge*lat"i*nate</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To be converted into
gelatin, or into a substance like jelly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Lapis lazuli, if calcined, does not effervesce, but
<qex>gelatinates</qex> with the mineral acids.</q>
<rj><qau>Kirwan.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

